precis:
Amendment to the TRANSPORTATION OF DANGEROUS GOODS REGULATIONS
Schedule No. 14 introducing requirements for the design, construction,
retesting, selection, use and handling of non-bulk packagings and cylinders
used for the transportation of dangerous goods by road, rail and domestic
marine.
